### Document Conflicts

Vector [batches](#buffers--batches) data flushes it to Elasticsearch's
[`_bulk` API endpoint][urls.elasticsearch_bulk]. All events are inserted
via the `index` action. Which, in the case of an conflict (document with the
same `id`), will add or _replace_ the document as necessary.


